WEBVTT

01:42.240 --> 01:47.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:51.320 --> 01:53.720
The air is dry.

01:53.800 --> 01:56.800
Beware of fire.

02:02.880 --> 02:04.920
I've seen enough of this sort of thing.

02:06.080 --> 02:07.560
There's really no need to rush like this.

02:08.360 --> 02:10.360
Silly girl. What do you know?

02:11.480 --> 02:14.280
A man's prime fades faster than a woman's.
Do you understand?

02:14.360 --> 02:17.320
When they're young,
they've got the urge but not the courage.

02:17.400 --> 02:18.440
They're poor.

02:18.520 --> 02:20.960
In their prime, they've got the courage
but no time for the urge.

02:21.040 --> 02:22.080
They're busy.

02:23.040 --> 02:25.920
And by the time they finally have both,
the chance is long gone.

02:27.720 --> 02:29.520
Don't delay. Once there's a child,

02:29.600 --> 02:31.000
things will settle.

02:32.680 --> 02:34.200
Mrs. Zhao.

02:35.440 --> 02:36.560
All right, all right.

02:37.080 --> 02:38.440
I'll give you another trick.

02:40.120 --> 02:42.440
That bedding you spread
on the floor in your bridal room,

02:43.040 --> 02:44.600
I washed it for you today.

02:46.040 --> 02:48.360
You think he'll let you
sleep bare like that?

03:37.080 --> 03:37.920
Come here.

03:40.080 --> 03:43.040
I… Why?

03:45.440 --> 03:46.720
There's only one quilt.

03:47.480 --> 03:49.080
If you don't sleep here,

03:49.160 --> 03:50.520
you'll catch cold in the night.

03:51.840 --> 03:52.960
I can handle the cold.

04:04.560 --> 04:05.400
Come here.

04:18.560 --> 04:19.880
If you don't,

04:20.880 --> 04:22.960
Mrs. Zhao won't sleep a wink.

04:30.920 --> 04:32.880
Just as I thought.

04:33.640 --> 04:35.240
She'll end up on the bed.

04:35.880 --> 04:37.560
All these shameless tricks.

04:37.640 --> 04:39.680
If she catches a chill,
I'll have another patient to tend.

04:40.560 --> 04:42.160
You've spit all over me.

04:50.680 --> 04:51.840
Don't worry.

04:52.640 --> 04:54.320
I have no improper thoughts.

05:02.680 --> 05:04.600
And don't blame Mrs. Zhao for meddling.

05:05.920 --> 05:07.200
She means well.

05:10.680 --> 05:11.520
I know.

05:39.840 --> 05:41.080
What are you doing?

05:41.160 --> 05:43.280
If we're putting on a show,
we might as well do it properly.

05:44.600 --> 05:45.440
Let's not

05:45.960 --> 05:48.520
have Mr. and Mrs. Zhao
waiting outside all night.

05:56.800 --> 05:57.920
There we are.

05:59.200 --> 06:03.080
When we were young,
we had the urge but not the nerve.

06:03.160 --> 06:04.640
Now that we're older,

06:04.720 --> 06:06.800
we've got the nerve but not the urge.

06:06.880 --> 06:08.360
From what I see,

06:08.440 --> 06:12.520
young people these days have both.

06:13.720 --> 06:15.240
I only said that casually.

06:15.320 --> 06:17.360
You turned it into a whole speech.

06:19.080 --> 06:19.920
Wait a moment.

06:20.600 --> 06:21.960
You old coot.

06:22.840 --> 06:24.120
You were eavesdropping on us.

06:24.200 --> 06:25.280
I…

06:26.080 --> 06:27.800
The pot calling the kettle black.

06:27.880 --> 06:28.800
You're listening too.

06:28.880 --> 06:31.040
I enjoy it. What's it to you?

06:31.120 --> 06:32.120
You…

06:41.640 --> 06:42.920
After Master Sun arrived,

06:43.000 --> 06:44.600
I finally understood where you come from.

06:46.480 --> 06:49.200
You'll leave sooner or later, won't you?

06:55.640 --> 06:56.840
I won't cling to you.

06:58.680 --> 07:00.840
If you wish to leave,
you may go at any time.

07:03.280 --> 07:04.480
For now,

07:05.720 --> 07:06.720
I can't leave just yet.

07:12.520 --> 07:13.520
That's fine.

07:19.680 --> 07:21.000
There are things I must do.

07:23.160 --> 07:26.240
I need to stay to do them.

07:32.840 --> 07:35.280
I'll go on top. You get some rest.

07:42.560 --> 07:43.680
All right.

08:13.240 --> 08:15.760
There's still half a bowl
of braised rice in the kitchen.

08:15.840 --> 08:17.520
Are you hungry? I'll go warm it.

08:19.440 --> 08:20.400
I'm not hungry.

08:26.200 --> 08:27.880
I wonder if Ning is sleeping well.

08:28.680 --> 08:30.480
She always kicks her quilt off at night.

08:31.200 --> 08:34.200
-And I still need to feed the gyrfalcon.
-If you don't mind talking…

08:36.880 --> 08:38.039
may I ask you something?

08:40.480 --> 08:41.600
Go on.

08:43.720 --> 08:46.920
What were your parents like?

08:48.080 --> 08:48.920
Good people.

08:50.040 --> 08:50.920
How did they treat you?

08:53.000 --> 08:54.520
Like any parents

08:54.600 --> 08:56.200
treat their own child.

08:58.080 --> 08:59.440
If one day

09:00.920 --> 09:02.200
they meant to harm you,

09:03.880 --> 09:04.840
what would you do?

09:11.880 --> 09:14.920
When I was little,
my mother used to beat me often.

09:15.560 --> 09:17.200
Left hand, right hand,

09:18.120 --> 09:20.240
no restraint. It hurt terribly.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.360
But afterward,

09:21.960 --> 09:24.680
she still bought sweets for Ning and me.

09:26.880 --> 09:30.360
That isn't the sort of conflict I mean.

09:33.000 --> 09:33.880
I know.

09:36.080 --> 09:37.520
What I mean is,

09:39.600 --> 09:40.920
those who are truly close to you

09:41.840 --> 09:43.760
would never really harm you.

09:45.200 --> 09:48.920
Even if there are quarrels or bumps,

09:49.480 --> 09:50.320
afterward,

09:51.040 --> 09:52.960
they still slip you sweets
to make up for it.

09:57.360 --> 09:58.880
But if someone

09:59.640 --> 10:00.880
truly intends to hurt you,

10:02.480 --> 10:03.800
then at the root,

10:04.560 --> 10:06.560
that person was never truly close to you.

10:40.800 --> 10:42.280
You ate candied tangerine peel?

10:43.480 --> 10:45.640
I can smell it on you.

10:45.720 --> 10:46.800
You had a nightmare?

10:51.000 --> 10:52.280
Something sweet

10:53.640 --> 10:54.960
helps me sleep.

10:57.400 --> 11:00.440
If you want more later,
I'll buy it for you.

11:04.960 --> 11:06.160
Right now,

11:08.520 --> 11:09.400
do you want some?

13:35.080 --> 13:37.200
What exactly are you looking for
in the Fan household?

13:59.800 --> 14:00.960
Master Li?

14:07.440 --> 14:08.480
Come with me.

14:09.440 --> 14:10.440
No need.

14:12.480 --> 14:13.520
Take them down.

14:22.040 --> 14:23.240
I'll ask you one last time.

14:23.840 --> 14:25.440
What does the Fan family possess

14:26.240 --> 14:28.880
that would warrant the Wei clan's
Xuan Tie death warriors?

14:29.680 --> 14:32.160
Who are you? How do you know I'm…

14:38.880 --> 14:41.360
Marquis Wu'an. What are you doing here?

14:43.800 --> 14:45.480
I've broken the silence

14:46.760 --> 14:48.600
of countless military spies.

14:49.880 --> 14:51.720
If you'd like to test your resolve,

14:53.120 --> 14:54.640
I can make you the next.

14:55.720 --> 14:58.320
The Chancellor ordered me
to retrieve a letter.

14:58.400 --> 14:59.560
What letter?

15:05.760 --> 15:06.600
Speak.

15:08.640 --> 15:10.720
Your Lordship knows full well
the Chancellor's methods.

15:11.320 --> 15:14.120
Why trouble a small man like me?

15:14.960 --> 15:16.400
What else did he say?

15:27.600 --> 15:29.640
-Ms. Fan, are you hurt?
-Master Li…

15:30.920 --> 15:32.080
No.

15:33.440 --> 15:36.000
May I ask, Officer, your honorable name?

15:36.080 --> 15:38.120
We must set up
a longevity tablet in thanks.

15:39.640 --> 15:41.320
It's merely my duty. No need for that.

15:46.040 --> 15:48.320
My lord serves
as Zhenwei Commandant of Jizhou.

15:48.400 --> 15:49.920
His name is Li Huai'an.

15:53.080 --> 15:53.960
We are deeply grateful.

15:56.440 --> 15:58.520
You're too kind.
The rebels have grown bold.

15:58.600 --> 16:01.400
After Governor He of Jizhou
rode to Lucheng to defend the pass,

16:01.480 --> 16:03.520
I was dispatched here
to aid in suppressing bandits.

16:05.640 --> 16:08.640
But why would these
black-clad men pursue you?

16:08.720 --> 16:10.040
I truly do not know.

16:13.720 --> 16:15.400
Oh no. Yan Zheng!

16:18.160 --> 16:19.000
Follow her.

16:27.960 --> 16:29.280
Changyu's back.

16:32.760 --> 16:33.880
Changyu!

16:34.680 --> 16:36.120
Are you and Yan Zheng hurt?

16:36.200 --> 16:38.480
-What about the bodies at the gate?
-We're fine.

16:38.560 --> 16:39.560
Look after Changning, Mrs. Zhao.

16:39.640 --> 16:41.560
-All right.
-Don't let her see this.

16:41.640 --> 16:44.760
Go inside. Stay inside.

16:44.840 --> 16:45.680
Sir, you are…

16:49.080 --> 16:51.320
You're the gentleman who came before.

16:51.400 --> 16:53.400
I've been sent from Jizhou to investigate.

16:54.000 --> 16:56.360
Sir, you must get to the bottom of this.

16:56.440 --> 16:59.160
-The Fan family has suffered enough.
-Exactly.

17:04.520 --> 17:05.359
Yan Zheng.

17:08.560 --> 17:10.359
Move! Yan Zheng.

17:10.440 --> 17:12.920
Yan Zheng! Wake up!

17:13.000 --> 17:14.119
Get up.

17:14.200 --> 17:15.040
Get up.

17:17.839 --> 17:19.079
-Yan Zheng.
-Changyu.

17:19.160 --> 17:20.000
Changyu…

17:21.319 --> 17:23.160
Mr. Zhao, he needs help.

17:23.760 --> 17:24.760
Don't move him.

17:24.839 --> 17:26.760
You'll worsen his wounds.

17:27.640 --> 17:29.760
Let me check.

17:33.800 --> 17:36.360
Yan Zheng, wake up. Yan Zheng.

17:55.520 --> 17:58.040
This man and the black-clad ones below…

17:58.120 --> 17:59.520
Were they all killed by your husband?

18:02.680 --> 18:04.320
My husband used to escort caravans.

18:04.920 --> 18:06.000
He knows some martial arts.

18:07.400 --> 18:08.400
Officer,

18:08.480 --> 18:10.760
you must seek justice for us.

18:10.840 --> 18:12.720
This girl has had a hard life.

18:12.800 --> 18:14.880
Her parents passed just last month.

18:14.960 --> 18:17.520
She finally took in a husband.

18:17.600 --> 18:18.880
Now,

18:18.960 --> 18:21.240
he's wounded by these villains.

18:21.320 --> 18:23.440
If their origins aren't uncovered,

18:24.120 --> 18:26.880
how can she live in peace?

18:26.960 --> 18:28.840
My lord. My…

18:28.920 --> 18:30.200
There's a survivor below.

18:31.960 --> 18:33.120
-Rest assured.
-All right.

18:36.520 --> 18:38.240
Mr. Zhao, look again.

18:38.800 --> 18:39.920
Let me check once more.

18:40.000 --> 18:41.560
Once more.

18:42.440 --> 18:45.280
My lord,
that live-in husband is suspicious.

18:45.360 --> 18:46.760
Should we bring him in for questioning?

18:46.840 --> 18:48.240
No rush. I know what I'm doing.

18:48.320 --> 18:50.120
Let's question the survivor first.

18:50.200 --> 18:51.120
-Understood.
-This way.

18:54.720 --> 18:55.720
If I had known,

18:56.480 --> 18:58.200
I would have written you a divorce letter

18:59.440 --> 19:00.920
and sent you elsewhere to recover.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.960
You wouldn't have suffered this.

19:09.880 --> 19:14.600
My orders were to kill
the women of the Fan household

19:14.680 --> 19:16.720
and take the letter back.

19:16.800 --> 19:18.240
The letter?

19:27.320 --> 19:28.360
Fan Changyu.

20:23.880 --> 20:26.200
He's covered in blood.

20:27.000 --> 20:29.200
It looks dire.

20:29.760 --> 20:33.200
Yet his pulse is steady.

20:34.000 --> 20:35.720
He's lost so much blood.

20:39.440 --> 20:40.640
Strange.

20:41.240 --> 20:43.160
There are no fresh wounds.

20:43.760 --> 20:44.680
This blood…

20:45.240 --> 20:47.560
It's from old injuries reopening.

20:48.720 --> 20:50.320
Let me see his back.

20:51.560 --> 20:52.840
You're awake?

20:53.720 --> 20:55.120
Yan Zheng, you're awake?

21:02.440 --> 21:03.680
I'm fine.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.920
It's not my blood.

21:06.000 --> 21:07.440
Help him onto the bed.

21:08.720 --> 21:09.600
Careful.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.920
Slowly.

21:18.080 --> 21:18.960
Good.

21:20.480 --> 21:21.840
Good.

21:35.240 --> 21:36.280
Yan Zheng.

21:40.120 --> 21:42.560
Don't worry. I'm all right.

21:49.080 --> 21:51.960
Changyu, the officers want your statement.

21:55.320 --> 21:56.280
Go.

21:59.240 --> 22:00.240
Take care.

22:10.440 --> 22:11.280
TRAVEL PASS

22:11.360 --> 22:12.200
YAN ZHENG OF YAN VILLAGE,
CHANGLE COUNTY, XUZHOU,

22:12.280 --> 22:13.160
AN ESCORT GUARD EN ROUTE TO CHONGZHOU,
STRANDED IN LIN'AN, QINGPING, JIZHOU

22:13.240 --> 22:14.840
AFTER A BANDIT ATTACK.
A TRAVEL PASS IS HEREBY REISSUED.

22:14.920 --> 22:16.240
SUBMITTED BY FAN CHANGYU,
XIGU ALLEY, LIN'AN TOWN

22:20.960 --> 22:21.880
Changyu.

22:23.080 --> 22:25.080
What does a Zhenwei Commandant do?

22:27.320 --> 22:29.360
Madam, my surname is Li.

22:30.120 --> 22:32.360
-Lord Li.
-Lord Li.

22:33.360 --> 22:34.760
We thought

22:34.840 --> 22:36.880
you were a scholar before.

22:36.960 --> 22:38.960
Who knew you were
a high officer from Jizhou?

22:40.000 --> 22:41.360
I came

22:41.440 --> 22:43.440
to uncover these criminals

22:43.520 --> 22:44.440
and restore justice.

22:51.680 --> 22:53.240
The survivor's been taken in
for questioning.

22:55.360 --> 22:57.200
Stay home and wait for word.

22:57.280 --> 22:58.440
Once the case is concluded,

22:58.520 --> 22:59.960
the authorities will inform you.

23:00.640 --> 23:01.600
Lord Li,

23:01.680 --> 23:04.000
what if those people
come back for revenge?

23:04.080 --> 23:06.800
I know it's improper
to question an ongoing investigation,

23:06.880 --> 23:08.440
but my sister is still young.

23:09.640 --> 23:12.760
I planned to leave Lin'an after
the Spring Festival to avoid trouble.

23:14.440 --> 23:15.680
You intend to leave Lin'an?

23:20.800 --> 23:21.920
Was that your husband's idea?

23:22.640 --> 23:24.640
It was mine.
I am the head of this household.

23:26.720 --> 23:27.560
Leaving

23:28.960 --> 23:31.320
is only to prevent something like tonight
from happening again.

23:33.040 --> 23:35.160
Your parents and your uncle
were murdered in succession.

23:35.240 --> 23:37.240
You are not only the victim.
You are also a witness.

23:37.320 --> 23:39.160
Until this case is fully resolved,

23:39.240 --> 23:40.480
you may not leave Lin'an.

23:42.640 --> 23:45.320
That said,
I will increase patrols in the village.

23:45.400 --> 23:47.160
Until the matter is concluded,

23:47.240 --> 23:49.360
you and your family
will be under official protection.

23:50.280 --> 23:52.200
Lord Li,
you are truly a living bodhisattva.

23:52.280 --> 23:54.160
With those words,
we can finally rest easy.

23:54.840 --> 23:57.680
Search! Every house. Quickly!

23:58.280 --> 23:59.760
Within my jurisdiction,

23:59.840 --> 24:03.680
I will not allow
a single innocent to be harmed.

24:03.760 --> 24:06.120
Today, the people
will have an explanation.

24:06.200 --> 24:07.840
Search carefully.

24:08.440 --> 24:10.160
Let no criminal slip away.

24:10.240 --> 24:11.200
-Yes, sir.
-Yes.

24:16.680 --> 24:17.520
Lord Li.

24:20.400 --> 24:21.880
This humble official greets Lord Li.

24:23.320 --> 24:26.000
Upon hearing there was unrest
in Xigu Alley,

24:26.080 --> 24:27.920
I led men here to capture the culprits.

24:28.000 --> 24:29.720
I did not expect to encounter you here.

24:29.800 --> 24:31.920
Forgive my failure
to receive you properly.

24:33.160 --> 24:34.360
Your Honor!

24:34.920 --> 24:35.880
Your Honor.

24:38.280 --> 24:39.120
Your Honor.

24:40.040 --> 24:43.000
We found a spirit tablet
for Marquis Wu'an in this courtyard.

24:43.080 --> 24:43.920
Please take a look.

24:45.480 --> 24:46.960
Such audacity.

24:47.040 --> 24:48.880
Daring to privately worship Marquis Wu'an.

24:49.560 --> 24:50.400
Look, Your Honor.

24:52.440 --> 24:54.360
‎MARQUIS WU'AN XIE ZHENG

24:54.960 --> 24:56.000
Who?

24:56.080 --> 24:56.960
Whose residence is this?

24:58.960 --> 25:01.320
Your Honor, this is my home.

25:02.000 --> 25:03.240
You…

25:03.320 --> 25:04.600
Fan Changyu.

25:05.120 --> 25:06.040
You again?

25:06.120 --> 25:07.720
Your Honor,

25:07.800 --> 25:09.600
is there a law in Dayin forbidding

25:09.680 --> 25:10.840
the worship of Marquis Wu'an?

25:12.040 --> 25:13.040
Insolent woman.

25:13.120 --> 25:14.640
You dare talk back?

25:14.720 --> 25:16.600
Men. Seize her.

25:16.680 --> 25:18.040
Take the tablet with you.

25:18.120 --> 25:20.640
This time, you are caught
with both witness and evidence.

25:20.720 --> 25:22.200
Why have I never heard that the court

25:22.280 --> 25:24.280
-forbids honoring Marquis Wu'an?
-Well…

25:26.640 --> 25:28.800
You earned distinction
in both civil examinations.

25:28.880 --> 25:32.720
Surely you know his past actions have
long been condemned by the civil scholars.

25:35.400 --> 25:37.720
I have even heard Grand Tutor Li

25:37.800 --> 25:39.320
disapproved of the city massacre--

25:39.400 --> 25:42.160
The merits and faults of Marquis Wu'an
are for history to judge.

25:43.520 --> 25:44.800
He fought for the realm.

25:45.400 --> 25:46.600
In death, he remains honored.

25:53.040 --> 25:54.440
This…

25:56.080 --> 25:57.120
Worship is not a crime.

26:03.600 --> 26:04.840
Thank you, Lord Li.

26:08.840 --> 26:11.640
Your words have opened my eyes.

26:12.200 --> 26:13.680
It seems my understanding was too narrow.

26:14.840 --> 26:15.960
In that case,

26:16.040 --> 26:17.560
Lord Li, please return to town first.

26:17.640 --> 26:19.360
Allow me to report the case details.

26:19.440 --> 26:20.800
-Lord Li, this way.
-After you.

26:23.240 --> 26:24.480
Please. This way.

26:31.680 --> 26:34.880
NORTHWEST POST STATION

26:35.840 --> 26:37.160
Careful, my lord.

26:37.240 --> 26:38.280
The steps.

26:44.240 --> 26:45.920
General Zhuo,
no need to escort me further.

26:46.600 --> 26:48.120
Forgive us for not seeing you farther.

26:55.080 --> 26:57.320
Tell me. This Li Huai'an.

26:57.400 --> 26:59.480
From beginning to end,
his face never softened.

27:00.480 --> 27:01.320
Why is that?

27:02.040 --> 27:04.360
Grand Tutor Li's faction
and Chancellor Wei's faction

27:04.440 --> 27:05.760
have been at odds for years.

27:05.840 --> 27:07.760
The entire court knows it.

27:07.840 --> 27:09.160
Yet today,

27:09.240 --> 27:11.640
Lord Li defended Marquis Wu'an.

27:11.720 --> 27:12.560
Exactly.

27:13.680 --> 27:14.800
Think about it.

27:15.360 --> 27:17.560
If they were truly enemies,

27:18.320 --> 27:20.120
why would Grand Tutor Li

27:20.200 --> 27:22.120
allow his eldest grandson

27:22.200 --> 27:24.480
to study under He Jingyuan
of the Wei faction?

27:26.160 --> 27:27.080
That happened?

27:28.080 --> 27:30.640
Could there have been ties
before all this?

27:34.240 --> 27:37.080
Who can ever truly grasp
the minds of powerful ministers?

27:39.720 --> 27:40.640
As for me,

27:41.320 --> 27:43.160
stuck in this remote county,

27:43.240 --> 27:44.800
by the time word reaches Lin'an,

27:44.880 --> 27:46.440
it's nothing but hot air.

27:48.520 --> 27:49.600
And this mess is your fault.

27:49.680 --> 27:50.720
You were the one

27:50.800 --> 27:52.040
who suggested currying favor.

27:52.120 --> 27:53.880
Now we've flattered the wrong side.

27:53.960 --> 27:55.320
Yes, yes.

27:55.400 --> 27:56.280
I deserve punishment.

27:56.360 --> 27:57.520
-I deserve punishment.
-Enough.

27:58.160 --> 27:59.520
We'll return and reconsider carefully.

28:02.200 --> 28:04.760
At last, that fawning magistrate is gone.

28:06.080 --> 28:08.280
My lord, we've confirmed

28:08.360 --> 28:10.680
each assassin carried a Xuan Tie whistle.

28:15.360 --> 28:17.840
Xuan Tie whistle.
Originating from the capital.

28:18.680 --> 28:20.720
If exposed, they take their own lives.

28:23.080 --> 28:25.640
It matches the reputation
of Wei faction death warriors.

28:27.640 --> 28:29.000
Who would have thought Marquis Wu'an,

28:30.080 --> 28:32.280
whom we searched for on the battlefield,

28:34.080 --> 28:35.680
would be hiding in Lin'an
as a live-in husband?

28:37.120 --> 28:39.840
What? He is Marquis Wu'an?

28:39.920 --> 28:40.880
Impossible.

28:41.480 --> 28:43.800
The Marquis's temper was famously fierce.

28:43.880 --> 28:45.440
Even if he were disgraced,

28:45.520 --> 28:47.760
even if His Majesty
cast him into the imperial prison

28:47.840 --> 28:50.160
and ordered him
to marry into the royal family,

28:50.240 --> 28:51.440
he would never have agreed.

28:51.520 --> 28:53.120
When we were young,

28:53.920 --> 28:56.000
we trained under our master
in arms and strategy.

28:57.600 --> 28:59.640
Though more than ten years have passed

29:01.200 --> 29:02.560
and his features have changed,

29:03.400 --> 29:04.320
I'm six in ten sure.

29:05.880 --> 29:07.000
Whether it is him or not,

29:07.960 --> 29:09.240
send a fast horse to Yanzhou.

29:09.760 --> 29:10.720
We'll know soon enough.

29:13.880 --> 29:16.200
XIGU ALLEY

29:19.840 --> 29:20.720
That's all I have.

29:21.240 --> 29:23.560
The harvest's been poor this year.

29:23.640 --> 29:24.880
It's the same everywhere.

29:26.760 --> 29:27.640
Yeah.

29:27.720 --> 29:30.360
Last year was decent.
Each year worse than the last.

29:31.880 --> 29:33.600
Have you heard?

29:33.680 --> 29:35.560
There's been another death
in the Fan family.

29:36.520 --> 29:37.840
After that girl supposedly

29:37.920 --> 29:39.760
brought misfortune
upon Fan Erniu and his wife,

29:39.840 --> 29:41.280
that household hasn't known peace.

29:42.760 --> 29:45.440
I heard her live-in husband
is gravely injured.

29:45.520 --> 29:48.920
Who knows if he'll even
function as a man again.

29:50.360 --> 29:52.720
Fan Changyu is cursed.

29:52.800 --> 29:54.240
Luckily Scholar Song

29:54.320 --> 29:57.200
broke off the engagement.
Otherwise, he would have suffered too.

29:57.280 --> 30:00.720
He is blessed by the God of Literature.
Fortunate destiny.

30:01.400 --> 30:02.240
Yes.

30:03.040 --> 30:04.160
Yes.

30:09.240 --> 30:10.080
Who are those two?

30:10.840 --> 30:11.880
Don't know.

30:16.280 --> 30:17.600
What are you doing?

30:17.680 --> 30:20.400
We should be asking you.
Where are you from?

30:20.480 --> 30:22.280
Why are you eavesdropping?

30:23.480 --> 30:24.800
We're from Jizhou Prefecture.

30:24.880 --> 30:27.600
We have prior ties with the Fan family.
Hearing their misfortune,

30:28.160 --> 30:29.240
we grew concerned.

30:30.720 --> 30:33.480
They just suffered calamity,
and strangers appear asking questions?

30:34.080 --> 30:35.960
Sounds suspicious to me.

30:36.040 --> 30:37.920
We should report them.

30:38.840 --> 30:41.200
They don't look like criminals.

30:42.040 --> 30:44.040
Criminals don't carry signs
on their faces.

30:44.640 --> 30:47.760
I wouldn't waste your time without reason.

30:55.960 --> 30:57.640
I know something. I'll tell you.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.040
I'll tell you.

31:01.120 --> 31:02.640
Zhenwei Commandant!

31:04.280 --> 31:05.640
Good morning, sirs.

31:05.720 --> 31:06.920
You're still in the village?

31:07.000 --> 31:07.920
I thought you left.

31:08.000 --> 31:08.840
He is what?

31:09.400 --> 31:10.400
What's happening here?

31:11.560 --> 31:13.160
Who did you just say they were?

31:13.760 --> 31:15.760
High officials from Jizhou.
Here on an investigation.

31:16.360 --> 31:17.440
High officials?

31:17.520 --> 31:18.960
I only wished to ask…

31:20.800 --> 31:21.600
I mean…

31:21.680 --> 31:23.320
-I don't know much.
-Here, take it back.

31:23.400 --> 31:24.880
-We haven't even asked yet.
-Honestly…

31:24.960 --> 31:26.080
Madam.

31:26.160 --> 31:28.480
Gentlemen, are you still buying?

31:32.320 --> 31:35.040
Mrs. Zhao, wait up.

31:35.800 --> 31:37.920
What exactly does that Commandant do?

31:39.320 --> 31:40.360
I don't know.

31:40.440 --> 31:42.920
But even the county magistrate
treated them with great respect.

31:45.640 --> 31:46.680
Ladies.

31:47.440 --> 31:48.640
-Don't ask us.
-We don't know.

31:48.720 --> 31:50.040
-We're not close with the Fans.
-No.

31:50.120 --> 31:51.160
Just one question!

32:12.520 --> 32:14.360
Sir, may I ask…

32:14.440 --> 32:16.160
No. I don't know.

32:23.040 --> 32:25.080
My lord, we did not uncover much.

32:25.160 --> 32:26.000
No one will speak plainly.

32:26.720 --> 32:28.920
Only that Fan Changyu
took in the outsider Yan Zheng

32:29.000 --> 32:30.920
to safeguard her family property.

32:31.000 --> 32:32.440
He was wounded by bandits

32:32.520 --> 32:33.680
and saved by her.

32:33.760 --> 32:35.880
According to the travel documents
we reviewed,

32:36.720 --> 32:37.680
there are no inconsistencies.

32:38.600 --> 32:41.080
If this was all carefully arranged
by Marquis Wu'an,

32:41.160 --> 32:42.440
we wouldn't uncover anything.

32:43.640 --> 32:45.160
Why not question the Zhaos again?

32:45.680 --> 32:47.240
Mrs. Zhao is sharp,

32:47.320 --> 32:48.720
but Mr. Zhao appears easier to handle.

32:50.080 --> 32:52.120
Given their closeness with Fan Changyu,

32:52.200 --> 32:53.400
their testimony may be biased.

32:54.000 --> 32:54.840
True.

32:59.960 --> 33:00.800
My lord.

33:06.240 --> 33:08.640
If you wish to hear
about the Fan household,

33:11.080 --> 33:12.880
I know quite a bit.

33:13.840 --> 33:14.960
It's just…

33:22.560 --> 33:23.520
My lord.

33:23.600 --> 33:25.920
Fan Changyu is born under a calamity star.

33:26.520 --> 33:28.320
She brought ruin to her own parents,

33:28.400 --> 33:30.120
and even her uncle died under her shadow.

33:30.800 --> 33:35.200
And that husband she brought
into the house, handsome enough, yes,

33:35.720 --> 33:38.440
but not a shred of backbone.

33:39.280 --> 33:40.520
On their wedding day,

33:40.600 --> 33:43.360
in front of the whole village,
he swore he would obey Fan Changyu.

33:43.440 --> 33:45.240
Living under a woman's roof.

33:45.320 --> 33:49.200
You're saying he publicly acknowledged
Fan Changyu as head of the household?

33:50.120 --> 33:51.920
Everyone saw it. Everyone heard it.

33:52.000 --> 33:53.880
I'm not spinning tales.

33:57.560 --> 33:59.880
My lord,
I'll let you in on something else.

34:01.400 --> 34:02.760
Fan Changyu

34:02.840 --> 34:06.400
and her so-called husband
are likely putting on a show.

34:06.480 --> 34:08.000
They've never even shared a bed.

34:08.679 --> 34:11.560
She's still untouched.

34:13.080 --> 34:14.159
Do not foul my lord's ears

34:14.760 --> 34:15.960
with such talk.

34:16.639 --> 34:17.480
It's fine.

34:18.080 --> 34:18.920
Please continue.

34:19.000 --> 34:21.239
What's there to blush about?

34:21.320 --> 34:25.000
That girl's brow hasn't opened.
Her steps are light and unburdened.

34:25.080 --> 34:27.800
If she's not a maiden, then what is she?

34:27.880 --> 34:29.960
That will do. We have heard enough.

34:30.040 --> 34:30.880
Thank you for your candor.

34:33.159 --> 34:34.040
My lord, my lord.

34:36.679 --> 34:38.199
Please do not let anyone know

34:38.280 --> 34:40.120
I was the one who told you.

34:40.199 --> 34:41.520
You know,

34:41.600 --> 34:43.840
Fan Changyu was raised a butcher.

34:43.920 --> 34:46.639
-She's strong enough to break bones.
-We are well aware.

34:48.440 --> 34:49.400
-My lord…
-That's enough.

34:49.480 --> 34:50.400
-Thank you.
-I wasn't--

34:50.480 --> 34:51.360
Thank you, madam.

34:51.960 --> 34:54.280
-No need to follow.
-I wasn't finished.

34:56.520 --> 34:57.600
You expect me to believe

34:57.680 --> 35:00.080
Marquis Wu'an married into her family
and called her master?

35:00.600 --> 35:02.840
My lord. What are your odds now?

35:04.480 --> 35:05.440
Seven parts in ten.

35:07.840 --> 35:09.040
Seven?

35:09.120 --> 35:10.240
That is more than before.

35:10.760 --> 35:12.840
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE, JIZHOU YAMEN

35:12.920 --> 35:15.360
The terrain east of Chongzhou
is steep and treacherous.

35:15.440 --> 35:17.240
Easy to defend, hard to breach.
A natural fortress.

35:17.920 --> 35:20.080
If they entrench there,
our forces will struggle to advance.

35:20.160 --> 35:21.280
VIRTUE COMMANDS LOYALTY

35:21.360 --> 35:24.880
General, we might take the ravine path
through Heng Mountain,

35:24.960 --> 35:26.120
circle around,

35:26.200 --> 35:27.840
and strike their flank or rear,

35:27.920 --> 35:29.960
bypassing their forward defenses entirely.

35:39.200 --> 35:40.880
A yamen that conducts official business,

35:41.480 --> 35:43.240
yet its doors are shut tight
in broad daylight.

35:43.840 --> 35:47.320
Or is it General He
has matters he prefers unseen?

35:47.400 --> 35:48.360
WEI XUAN, SON OF WEI YAN

35:51.800 --> 35:53.920
Why is Li Huai'an in Lin'an?

35:55.440 --> 35:58.920
Is Li Xing trying to stir trouble
for my family again?

36:01.080 --> 36:03.680
Bandits are rampant near Lin'an.

36:04.280 --> 36:05.560
I sent him to suppress them.

36:06.160 --> 36:08.760
He happened upon a homicide in town.

36:08.840 --> 36:10.400
That delayed him a few days.

36:10.480 --> 36:12.480
Once resolved, he will return.

36:12.560 --> 36:13.840
General He,

36:15.320 --> 36:17.200
stop shielding your prized student.

36:17.280 --> 36:19.560
A mere sixth rank commandant

36:20.080 --> 36:22.240
rushing off to some remote town
to hunt bandits.

36:24.200 --> 36:26.920
He is clearly using it as cover
to smear my family!

36:28.240 --> 36:29.520
Wei Xuan, weigh your words.

36:30.760 --> 36:34.520
Wei Xuan, you already
command Yanzhou's troops.

36:35.200 --> 36:36.640
Why divert to Jizhou?

36:36.720 --> 36:39.280
What do you want with me?

36:42.080 --> 36:43.880
Xie Zheng was always unruly.

36:44.680 --> 36:47.640
His soldiers will not submit easily.

36:49.320 --> 36:50.560
If I assume control,

36:52.600 --> 36:53.960
mistakes may follow.

36:57.080 --> 36:58.120
General He.

36:59.680 --> 37:02.360
Help me bring the Yanzhou troops to heel.

37:02.440 --> 37:05.720
We press forward and seize Chongzhou
from Prince Changxin.

37:05.800 --> 37:06.920
Once the great work is done,

37:07.920 --> 37:10.600
you and I will stand foremost
before my father.

37:15.840 --> 37:17.000
Xie Xuan,

37:17.080 --> 37:20.920
Prince Changxin suffered setbacks
because of Marquis Wu'an

37:21.000 --> 37:22.360
and lost several major battles.

37:22.960 --> 37:24.600
He has retreated to Chongzhou,

37:25.200 --> 37:27.280
but he is far from broken.

37:27.360 --> 37:28.680
His capable generals remain.

37:29.400 --> 37:31.680
Xie Xuan, you have traveled far.

37:31.760 --> 37:33.640
This is not the time for reckless action.

37:33.720 --> 37:35.160
On the contrary.

37:35.760 --> 37:38.160
After Prince Changxin's repeated defeats,

37:38.240 --> 37:39.640
Chongzhou's morale must be low.

37:39.720 --> 37:40.960
Now is the time to strike!

37:45.200 --> 37:46.080
General He.

37:46.680 --> 37:49.040
I respect you
as Father's veteran commander,

37:49.600 --> 37:51.960
so I came personally.

37:52.680 --> 37:55.360
This is an order. Not a discussion.

37:59.720 --> 38:01.800
I expect your cooperation.

38:18.120 --> 38:19.000
Chancellor Wei.

38:19.080 --> 38:20.080
DAYIN

38:22.080 --> 38:23.600
What is the matter, Grand Tutor Li?

38:23.680 --> 38:24.520
Chancellor Wei,

38:24.600 --> 38:26.320
in the Battle of Jinzhou,

38:26.400 --> 38:27.840
Commander Xie Linshan fell.

38:27.920 --> 38:30.920
More than a decade later,
his son, Marquis Wu'an, is missing.

38:32.000 --> 38:35.320
Yet you still sent
your only legitimate son

38:35.400 --> 38:36.840
to the northwest.

38:37.920 --> 38:40.520
If we speak of loyalty to Dayin,

38:40.600 --> 38:43.760
none surpass you, Chancellor Wei.

38:44.440 --> 38:48.640
Though the realm is vast,
not an inch of soil may be yielded.

38:49.280 --> 38:52.880
The sons of both Wei and Xie
died on that battlefield.

38:53.480 --> 38:55.000
Without regret.

38:56.360 --> 39:00.040
Then we shall await
your eldest son's triumphant return.

39:00.560 --> 39:04.440
Allow me to congratulate you in advance.

39:06.200 --> 39:08.160
And I congratulate you, Grand Tutor Li.

39:08.240 --> 39:11.400
Your eldest grandson now
serves as Zhenwei Commandant.

39:11.480 --> 39:14.320
You sent him to the northwest
to train from youth.

39:14.400 --> 39:16.320
A most calculated move.

39:16.840 --> 39:18.280
When he returns,

39:19.040 --> 39:21.240
he will surely be a pillar of the realm.

39:24.200 --> 39:27.520
For 16 years, my loyalty
has remained unchanged.

39:27.600 --> 39:29.720
All I do is for Dayin.

39:29.800 --> 39:31.160
Open and upright.

39:31.840 --> 39:33.280
Open and upright?

39:33.880 --> 39:35.920
Sixteen years ago,

39:36.000 --> 39:39.600
those two words would have
crushed you, Grand Tutor Li.

39:47.680 --> 39:48.560
What…

39:48.640 --> 39:50.280
The northwest army belongs to Dayin.

39:50.360 --> 39:53.040
Does he think it belongs
to the Wei clan alone?

39:53.120 --> 39:55.000
Wei Yan grows ever more brazen!

40:34.320 --> 40:36.320
TO HIS EXCELLENCY, CHANCELLOR WEI OF DAYIN

40:36.400 --> 40:38.800
It is time to hand it over.

40:40.240 --> 40:42.400
When you entrusted this to me,

40:42.480 --> 40:44.360
you knew such a day would come.

40:45.720 --> 40:46.920
You wished me

40:47.760 --> 40:49.800
to safeguard your two daughters.

40:52.600 --> 40:53.480
Peiyi.

40:54.680 --> 40:56.040
Ride with urgent dispatch.

40:56.600 --> 40:58.840
Deliver this to Chancellor Wei.

40:59.600 --> 41:00.640
Yes.

41:08.000 --> 41:09.000
Come out.

41:09.600 --> 41:11.000
This afternoon in the council hall,

41:11.760 --> 41:14.640
I knew you were there.

41:19.840 --> 41:21.720
I feared the timing was improper.

41:22.360 --> 41:24.640
After all, my identity is delicate.

41:24.720 --> 41:25.680
Wenkan.

41:26.520 --> 41:28.040
I sent you to suppress bandits.

41:28.120 --> 41:29.680
What is there to fear?

41:30.880 --> 41:33.080
I feared my Li lineage
would draw criticism

41:33.160 --> 41:34.400
upon you.

41:34.960 --> 41:36.480
Showing myself would only
give Chancellor Wei

41:36.560 --> 41:38.040
something to talk about.

41:40.760 --> 41:41.960
Wenkan.

41:42.760 --> 41:44.240
Count the years.

41:44.920 --> 41:46.760
How long have you followed me?

41:46.840 --> 41:48.920
I followed you to the northwest as a child

41:49.000 --> 41:51.440
and studied the art of war under you.

41:51.520 --> 41:53.800
Sixteen years have passed.

41:55.640 --> 41:57.080
Then you should understand.

41:58.120 --> 41:59.680
In my eyes,

42:00.360 --> 42:03.640
there is no feud of Li and Wei.

42:03.720 --> 42:06.800
There is only Dayin's army

42:06.880 --> 42:08.280
and Dayin's people.

42:09.320 --> 42:12.280
If your conscience is clear,

42:12.360 --> 42:15.920
there is no need
to hide behind your surname.

42:19.680 --> 42:20.560
Now.

42:21.080 --> 42:23.960
The matter I asked you to investigate.
What have you found?

42:24.040 --> 42:25.080
I discovered

42:25.160 --> 42:28.160
that Chancellor Wei's death warriors
attacked the Fan household twice.

42:28.240 --> 42:29.960
Clearly, they were searching
for something.

42:30.040 --> 42:31.160
Fortunately,

42:31.240 --> 42:33.080
the lady of the house was unharmed.

42:33.160 --> 42:35.320
But the sisters have begun
considering leaving Lin'an.

42:36.040 --> 42:38.120
I stopped them
under the pretext of the investigation

42:38.200 --> 42:39.920
and placed Zhuo Ran
to guard them in secret.

42:40.000 --> 42:41.400
That will keep them safer.

42:41.480 --> 42:44.880
How are the sisters faring?

42:45.560 --> 42:48.560
They make their living butchering pigs.
They recently took in a live-in husband.

42:50.720 --> 42:51.560
Teacher.

42:52.360 --> 42:54.840
One more matter now has some shape.

42:58.680 --> 43:00.000
If Marquis Wu'an

43:00.520 --> 43:03.040
truly lives, what should be done?

45:40.640 --> 45:44.160
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:44.240 --> 45:45.160
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
